  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Jellies of the Deep</i> is a hidden object and spot-the-difference game in one. Visit secret spots below the ocean to find mystery one-of-a-kind <i>jellies</i> hiding in plain sight!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relaxed gameplay, no time limits</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20 colourful hand-drawn levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >60 cute creatures to collect & name</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Icon-based, no text gameplay (creature names in Latin alphabet)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Level up to larger maps with more creatures and new objects to interact with, such as lights and freeze mode.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Soothing music with ocean sounds</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One time purchase, no in-app purchases</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Very cosy and totally idie!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020970/extras/e0b7f906591a4ceb7f5ada9dab9bdc1f.poster.avif?t=1753747390\" width=616 height=121 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020970/extras/e0b7f906591a4ceb7f5ada9dab9bdc1f.webm?t=1753747390\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Jellies of the Deep</i> is a hidden object and spot-the-difference game in one. Visit secret spots below the ocean to find mystery one-of-a-kind <i>jellies</i> hiding in plain sight!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relaxed gameplay, no time limits</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20 colourful hand-drawn levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >60 cute creatures to collect & name</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Icon-based, no text gameplay (creature names in Latin alphabet)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Level up to larger maps with more creatures and new objects to interact with, such as lights and freeze mode.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Soothing music with ocean sounds</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One time purchase, no in-app purchases</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Very cosy and totally idie!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020970/extras/e0b7f906591a4ceb7f5ada9dab9bdc1f.poster.avif?t=1753747390\" width=616 height=121 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020970/extras/e0b7f906591a4ceb7f5ada9dab9bdc1f.webm?t=1753747390\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
